    "description": "<p>Your [Initiative] becomes 0 until the end of the Round. From your Sq, designate a Sq of [Target: Wide [SR x 2] (A) / Range: 4 Sq]. If you use a [Magic Attack] with [Target: Area] in the first main process of this round, the target of that attack will be changed to [Target: Things that exist in all designated Sq (A)].</p>\n<p></p>\n<p>A special skill that draws a three-dimensional magic formation by accumulating magical power around it while chanting. Dramatically increases the effective range of magic, but fine control becomes impossible.</p>",
